{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1939, "height": 2652, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "代洪武年间，由洪洞大槐树移民，杜氏兄弟四人号”破锅杜“，其一迁河南府渑池之坻坞西村，因名讳失传，讳称”流芳“，是为渑池杜氏初祖。二世分东西两门，四世被敕赐义民，五世析分为四派，至今居渑已六百余年，人口达三千多人。\n", "block_bbox": [188, 239, 1600, 462], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏旧有祠堂、宗谱，时当奥运之年，渑池杜氏由族人杜军、韶光倡议，平泉等人负责修复宗祠，增其规制，于十月初一日举行了杜氏宗祠及石旌柱修复竣工典礼，同时进行了隆重的祭祖活动：至祖坟告慰先祖，在宗祠进行揭牌仪式，高搭彩门，敲响社鼓，鞭炮齐鸣，宣读祭文，拜祭祖灵。焰火当晚燃放，曲剧三天助兴。此本图文集正是崤渑人文的写照，杜氏渊源的流胤，杜氏文化的实录。正所谓：文明兴盛千古事，尧后杜氏著青史，继绳踵武在我辈，六百荣光有绵祀。\n", "block_bbox": [186, 481, 1604, 881], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二00八年十一月十八世建成谨识", "block_bbox": [958, 905, 1604, 943], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "六、渑池杜氏碑刻辑录", "block_bbox": [663, 1019, 1131, 1064], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "大明国河南道河南府沔池县", "block_bbox": [272, 1144, 768, 1184], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "付村保西里人氏，见在北底坞镇西村居住等人杜门口氏同男杜真银妻李氏王氏安氏所保平安愿重修古刹台口碑\n", "block_bbox": [190, 1205, 1602, 1305], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "观音堂观三间，有口立菩萨三尊，一切诸佛口口口圣像完备同化住僧人孝经凡诸色匠人施财功德口成完备工碑少记后云。\n", "block_bbox": [191, 1326, 1603, 1426], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "观音菩萨一尊杜真金同妻杨氏记", "block_bbox": [274, 1445, 863, 1485], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "文殊菩萨一尊杜一枝同妻贺氏记", "block_bbox": [274, 1504, 864, 1546], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "普贤菩萨一尊杜自美同妻平氏、杨现同妻王氏□运仝认表", "block_bbox": [273, 1564, 1309, 1607], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "供给人：", "block_bbox": [273, 1623, 425, 1665], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "王仲金 陈群子卢天福杜一礼", "block_bbox": [273, 1685, 835, 1726], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "陈保□陈相□杜世□", "block_bbox": [284, 1746, 703, 1788], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "西底坞村生员王世隆王业新□生李正让等篆", "block_bbox": [192, 1808, 669, 1911], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "（以下14人名略）", "block_bbox": [393, 1932, 698, 1975], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "北底坞村郑顺（以下杜天渠、杜岳、杜直纯、杜和、杜一春、杜平等约50人名略）\n", "block_bbox": [189, 1992, 718, 2226], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "□□□□□□年仲冬十月廿一日立□匠人张断、张", "block_bbox": [190, 2241, 719, 2408], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [748, 1826, 1611, 2411], "block_id": 17, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1714, 702, 1786, 1369], "block_id": 18, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三七八", "block_bbox": [1727, 1997, 1776, 2113], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 18}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9818441271781921, "coordinate": [186.61798095703125, 481.32598876953125, 1604.308837890625, 881.9598999023438]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9752914905548096, "coordinate": [188.865478515625, 239.14044189453125, 1600.557861328125, 462.604248046875]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9656752943992615, "coordinate": [748.6470336914062, 1826.797607421875, 1611.3369140625, 2411.979736328125]}, {"